premise_source_doc_sentence: In One Piece , Luffy sails from the East Blue to the Grand Line in search of the legendary treasure One Piece to succeed Gol.D .
Outside the One Piece franchise , Luffy has had an appearance in the crossover manga Cross Epoch , and in a collaborative one-shot manga with Toriko .

Luffy is introduced in One Piece chapter 1 , first published in Japan 's Weekly Shōnen Jump magazine on July 19 , 1997 , as a young boy whose body gains the properties of rubber after he inadvertently eats a supernatural fruit called the Gum-Gum Fruit , one of many Devil Fruits that can be found in the universe .
In April 2007 , Funimation Entertainment acquired the license of One Piece from 4Kids and would use their in-house voice cast in preparation for the series ' DVD releases .
One Piece made its U.S. premiere on September 18 , 2004 , on the Fox network 's Fox Box programming block , and also began airing on the Cartoon Network 's Toonami block in April 2005 .
